org.dgfoundation.amp.nireports.testcases.generic

Class AbstractFundingColumn

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.dgfoundation.amp.nireports.testcases.generic.HardcodedCells<CategAmountCell>
      • org.dgfoundation.amp.nireports.testcases.generic.AbstractFundingColumn
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    DRCFundingCells, TanzaniaFundingCells, TestcasesFundingCells

    public abstract class AbstractFundingColumn
extends HardcodedCells<CategAmountCell>
    a Funding Column which gets its data from a source which encodes the cells independent of the schema. Supplies various utilities to be used by the concrete subclasses (which construct cells either from hardcoded-in-src data OR hardcoded-in-files data); also supplies a method for reading cells off a binary dump created through FundingColumnGenerator.binaryDump() (please see decodeCells(InputStream))
